      <description>&lt;p&gt;This book, the first in a series of three, tells my personal story leading up to the opening of the small school. It demonstrates some of the failings of the education system and highlights the need for alternative approaches. The story will appeal to childcare professionals, teachers, parents and anybody who enjoys reading memoirs and narrative non-fiction. Following its release as an ebook it received excellent reviews and became an Amazon Number 1 Best Seller.&lt;/p&gt;
